Steps.Text: Lift Off (LO) -2:55 (If no LO, start 1 REV before CM overhead passing)
MISSION TIMER - Set ([C] SYNC MET TIMERS)
Acq-8:00 or 8 minutes before CSM is overhead of the LM
Wait until CSM has passed landing location, or in final REV before LO
Copy Ascent Pads and take note of LO (liftoff) time.
Configure CB's Per PWR UP checklsit (append steps if needed)
Repeat test for PITCH and YAW
CDR ACA (Out-Of-Detent, Pasue 2 sec At null)
(Min Imp Check for CDR ACA To AGC, ACA Cold Fire)
CDR ACA (Defelct slowly, Pause 2 sec at null)
Verify CB's Per LAUNCH Configuration (append using RUN if needed)
GO To LM TIMELINE BOOK: ASCENT
